sentences.english: For example, think of a Frisbee.
sentences.chinese: 举个例子，就看看飞盘吧。

sentences.english: They are moving in the ocean like giant frisbees, two discs thrown into the air.
sentences.chinese: 他们正朝著大海就像巨大的飞盘，两盘扔到空中。

sentences.english: Kids flip frisbees while their elders chat.
sentences.chinese: 孩子们玩飞盘，大人聊天。

sentences.english: I didn't catch the Frisbee because the car was in the way.
sentences.chinese: 因为车挡在中间，所以我没有接住飞盘。

sentences.english: I've played Ultimate Frisbee out here on the Killian Court, so that was a lot of fun.
sentences.chinese: 我在基里安方庭玩“极限飞盘”，非常好玩。

sentences.english: I would have caught the Frisbee if the car had not been in the way.
sentences.chinese: 如果汽车没当在中间，我就能接住飞盘了。

sentences.english: The frisbee is a light plastic disc, shaped like a plate, thrown between players in a game.
sentences.chinese: 飞盘是一种碟形塑料盘，供游戏者互相抛扔玩耍。

sentences.english: Frisbee players must brush the Frisbee at waist level to do a behind-the-back Frisbee brush.
sentences.chinese: 飞碟选手必须刷牙腰部飞盘做幕后背飞盘刷。

sentences.english: Frisbee players must brush the Frisbee at waist level to do a behind-the-back Frisbee brush.

sentences.english: People play Frisbee, they play soccer.
Her foster owner brought her out and gave me her Frisbee.
sentences.chinese: 养主牵出它，递给我它爱玩的飞盘。

sentences.english: Keep the disc high enough so that the opposition can't catch it early.
sentences.chinese: 让飞盘飞的够高，那样对方就不能很早的抓出它。

sentences.english: Ultimate Frisbee is a popular game played on college campuses and professionally.
sentences.chinese: 极限飞盘是一项在大学校园受欢迎的专门比赛。

sentences.english: Hu I-chih of Frisbee World Magazine collects all kinds of frisbees .
sentences.chinese: 飞盘世界杂志社社长胡怡之收集的各式飞盘。
